Valve.VR.InteractionSystem.EnableAfterTime Class Reference

This class enables a GameObject after a certain amount of time has passed. It also gradually changes the transparency of child Image components and the exposure of the skybox over time. More...

Detailed Description

This class enables a GameObject after a certain amount of time has passed. It also gradually changes the transparency of child Image components and the exposure of the skybox over time.
